Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.16,0:01:20.56,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰かを悲しませてまで　笑えなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.71,0:01:31.31,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう言って彼女はうつむいてたんだ　夜に泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.04,0:01:38.90,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷たく貼り付いて　凍えている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.10,0:01:45.86,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降り続く現実に　傘などない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.44,0:01:52.60,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生きてゆくことが　戦いなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:01:56.33,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そんな理由だけで　閉じ込められた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.43,0:01:59.22,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Heart　My Story
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.38,0:02:06.71,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泪のムコウが見えるの　輝いている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.92,0:02:13.41,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小さな窓には　あの頃みたいに　青い空が映る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.68,0:02:20.16,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ah  ah　鳥のように　飛べはしないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.18,0:02:31.64,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰かを悲しませたとき　感じる痛み
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.77,0:02:33.42,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘れないように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:39.00,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そっと目を閉じて　泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.16,0:01:20.56,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在傷害別人之前　不必強顏歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.71,0:01:31.31,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說著她低下頭　在黑夜裡哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.04,0:01:38.90,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷黏合在一起　渾身僵硬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.10,0:01:45.86,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨下個不停　卻沒有傘來遮擋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.44,0:01:52.60,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己囚禁在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:01:56.33,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有戰鬥才能求生的因果之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.43,0:01:59.22,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心　我的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.38,0:02:06.71,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淚水的彼岸所見到的　是五彩光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.92,0:02:13.41,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小的窗口　映照出那時蔚藍的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.68,0:02:20.16,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　雖說不能像鳥兒一樣自由翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.18,0:02:31.64,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷害別人之後的那份心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.77,0:02:33.42,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不忘卻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:39.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕輕地閉上眼　哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:52.13,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}#24  BEYOND
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.77,0:00:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我們相互理解  才能築起未來！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.19,0:00:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣吧  路易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:12.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪走這未來的…正是Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:18.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引發戰爭是他們！ 扭曲世界的也是他們！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.56,0:00:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫沙慈的  就是因為你  準尉才…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.95,0:00:36.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然敢把中尉…！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:39.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.43,0:00:48.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特攻兵器！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.95,0:00:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就再也逃不掉了  Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.73,0:00:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣  這樣下去的話路易絲你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.96,0:00:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.61,0:01:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是為了消滅你們的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行——！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.70,0:02:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特瑞亞·埃德  你身為改革者…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.71,0:02:58.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯了  我們不是改革者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是為了促使改革者出現而被人為製造出來的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:06.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是改良者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:06.48,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（改良者：innovate，由伊奧利亞創造的可以使用腦量子波的\N生命體，李本茲據此稱自己為innovator。另外，由李本茲創造的\N克隆軍隊也被稱為innovate。該詞有創新、改革之意。）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.42,0:03:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把吠陀還給我們  李本茲·阿爾馬克
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.57,0:03:15.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果改良者進化了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.39,0:03:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:23.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經成為了超越改良者  成為真正的改革者的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:24.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡說八道！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:30.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一槍我不會故意打偏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:34.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？  為什麼你會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下武器投降吧  我不會為難你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.46,0:03:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比利  為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:47.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白嗎？  是為了實現永久的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.39,0:03:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而實現這一目標最大的障礙就是你們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.48,0:03:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說要接受改革者的支配嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:04:02.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被更優秀的存在所統帥  理論上這也是正確的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且為了引導人類而被創造出來的他們  也不會向我們索求什麼回報
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:11.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是很理想的關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.99,0:04:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話就會失去自由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全的自由便是對道德的放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.22,0:04:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其結果只有毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在有序的社會結構裡  人們都滿足於有限的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.02,0:04:28.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵守既定的規則也會比較安心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.19,0:04:31.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.27,0:04:36.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「實現根除戰爭」  究其本質  其實是你們在擾亂世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:43.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不明白  現在把世界交給改革者才是與真正根除戰爭維繫在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有史以來人們夢寐以求的理想鄉即將實現
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.78,0:04:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是由我們自己構築的未來根本沒有任何意義
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.61,0:05:02.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不由自己糾正過去犯下的錯誤的話  真正的未來是不會到來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.17,0:05:12.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真頑強啊  Celestial什麼什麼的傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混賬傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.34,0:05:18.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:24.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.73,0:05:26.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:34.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN-Archer被…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:35.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數量太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:41.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子殘量已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:05:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈  沙慈·克洛斯羅德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.16,0:06:00.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:04.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.02,0:06:05.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.00,0:06:08.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.99,0:06:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶上她到安全的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:12.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:13.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知…知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:18.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改革者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該說過的  我是超越了改革者的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.58,0:06:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會把吠陀交給你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:55.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  將要引導人類的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.04,0:07:04.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲  路易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:09.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲  路易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:12.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.89,0:07:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being…！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和媽媽的仇！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.14,0:07:26.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧  死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.52,0:07:31.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易…絲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.51,0:07:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙…慈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.66,0:07:49.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.56,0:07:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.47,0:08:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲  你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.07,0:08:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.03,0:08:12.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是成為純種的改革者的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:14.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少得意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.32,0:08:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希琳  使用TRANS-AM Attack
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:18.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.99,0:08:31.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.51,0:08:37.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了？  路易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.90,0:08:39.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.23,0:08:41.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲  路易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.82,0:08:42.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲  沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.10,0:08:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:08:58.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路…路易絲？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:09.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲——！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要戰鬥！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:16.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了以自己的意識構築未來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:25.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你…就不能明白呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.10,0:09:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里路亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.52,0:09:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死  到此為止了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話托勒密會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不行  不能放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜  菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:54.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導彈剩得不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩  琳達
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的生命…正在消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.59,0:10:09.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混賬傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.99,0:10:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事…怎能讓它發生啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什  什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.49,0:10:24.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種GN粒子是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.63,0:10:33.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這光  不是戰鬥產生的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.75,0:10:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.75,0:10:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那光芒是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.76,0:10:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.88,0:10:46.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:53.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這光一定是刹那戰鬥的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.49,0:10:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命的光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:10:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變吧  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.52,0:11:02.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替沒能將這一切改變的我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:06.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  為了創造未來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要改變——！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:16.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦…腦量子波被擾亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.42,0:11:18.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那台Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.02,0:11:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有那台Gundam存在的話  就算是我們也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:23.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不僅僅是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.09,0:11:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李傑尼·雷傑塔？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.76,0:11:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為純種的改革者的腦量子波與Twin-Drive聯動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純度增加的GN粒子能擴張人的意識
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達成完全的進化了嗎  刹那·F·清榮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是真正的改革者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:52.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？  這種不舒服的感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:53.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙… 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.89,0:11:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.93,0:11:59.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你這樣的傢伙把哥哥他們…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.91,0:12:02.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子是那傢伙的弟弟嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:06.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宰了你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.36,0:12:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.76,0:12:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老子就是老子！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滅了你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.43,0:12:22.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:24.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別分心  阿里路亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:25.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里路亞？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.02,0:12:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我看好瑪麗就行了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:37.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼  這種不可思議的現象？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.66,0:12:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦中居然有聲音直接響起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  比利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.89,0:12:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明知道你的心意  卻還向你撒嬌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不要  不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:56.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…為了實現永久的和平…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了這個才決定要戰鬥的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.42,0:13:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…  一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.66,0:13:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…明明一直愛著你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.26,0:13:33.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.56,0:13:35.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…安德烈少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:40.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有聲音  是佩麗絲中尉嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.11,0:13:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  即便繼續對你心存怨恨  最終找你報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.33,0:13:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校也一定不會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.09,0:13:53.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口！  你這個叛徒！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:58.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼把親生父親…  把上校…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.36,0:14:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人背叛了軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭報應也是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.99,0:14:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他所做的是破壞永久的和平的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校不是會做那種事的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  那傢伙是能對母親見死不救的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.00,0:14:13.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能相信嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:19.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不能相互理解呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…  那個人什麼都沒有說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:26.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有藉口  沒有謝罪 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.27,0:14:29.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不瞭解我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.12,0:14:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才殺了他  親手！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.90,0:14:39.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要上校理解你的話  為什麼不去理解上校呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.38,0:14:45.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校也一定在為你著想的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼那時候什麼也沒對我說？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:15:00.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不和我說的話  不是什麼都不明白嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不和我說的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:10.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:15.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵機已擊墜80%
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.53,0:15:16.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能鬆懈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.86,0:15:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.41,0:15:21.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.45,0:15:24.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了？  身上的疼痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.83,0:15:33.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈  沙慈…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:46.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈  我再也不…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.48,0:15:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼都不用說  我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.51,0:16:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  這種溫暖的光是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.05,0:16:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺心都快融化了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.27,0:16:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那…？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.31,0:16:21.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:24.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他心中的光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.19,0:16:27.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照亮未來的光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=================================
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.13,0:16:37.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吠陀的位置在…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:44.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅哈羅  機體拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:45.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解  瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的GN粒子是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.12,0:16:54.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把我的腦量子波擾亂了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等待這個時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.51,0:16:58.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李傑尼·雷傑塔？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:08.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的連接被吠陀拒絕了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.90,0:17:10.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你將系統…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.33,0:17:13.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李本茲  我不會讓你為所欲為的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.81,0:17:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  特瑞亞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.35,0:17:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fsp225}　{\fsp1}Trial Field{\r}\N啊  Se…Seraphim啟動了審判領域
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與吠陀連接的機體相繼停下來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吠陀的輔助斷開了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.04,0:17:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死的特瑞亞·埃德！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.15,0:17:57.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪回吠陀了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.10,0:18:00.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來  戰鬥就能結束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:01.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.29,0:18:05.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於用上那個了啊  特瑞亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.91,0:18:09.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.80,0:18:11.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特瑞亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:17.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.35,0:18:21.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事…  已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  阿里路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到  到底怎麼回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.03,0:18:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！ 給我動起來！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒資格責怪哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.29,0:18:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼也不能放過這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我等著！你這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你無路可逃了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:20.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…  就是這傢伙將爸爸  媽媽還有艾米都…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.77,0:19:27.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾  我們倆曾經心意相通吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.33,0:19:30.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經心意相通吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢貨！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:52.55,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I love you　I trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.05,0:19:58.29,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}君の孤独を分けてほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.62,0:20:03.28,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I love you　I trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:08.69,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}光でも闇でも
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.19,0:20:17.64,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}二人だから信じ合えるの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.95,0:20:21.57,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}離さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:52.55,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\fs18}愛你　相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.05,0:19:58.29,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\fs18}想分享你的孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.62,0:20:03.28,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\fs18}愛你　相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:08.69,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\fs18}無論是光明還是黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.19,0:20:17.64,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\fs18}因為我倆彼此信任
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.95,0:20:21.57,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)\an8\fs18}不要離開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.15,0:19:54.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞琉  多虧了你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才能明白人與人可以相互理解的世界並不是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.18,0:20:02.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  就算被世界疏遠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.36,0:20:04.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使身負罪責
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.49,0:20:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:13.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為Celestial Being的Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是吠陀的本體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.36,0:20:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…特瑞亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.11,0:20:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特瑞亞·埃德！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.74,0:20:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此仇必報！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.21,0:20:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼擅自就認為我已經死了可真是傷腦筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.07,0:20:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡  你在哪裡？特瑞亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我的意識已完全與吠陀相連
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吠陀？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.96,0:20:51.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很慶倖自己是改革者…  不  是改良者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.66,0:20:55.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這能力能夠拯救你們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:21:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我通過與吠陀相連  從而得知了所有的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:07.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就告訴你  伊奧利亞計劃的全貌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.41,0:22:33.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密  我暫時回來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.73,0:22:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.14,0:22:40.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞計劃…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.89,0:22:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的武力介入行動儘管自我矛盾  卻促成了世界的統合
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.14,0:22:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我們自身終會滅亡  也能使人類的意志得以統一
